data.description: Stunning home with amazing views  of South Mountain.  Far enough away from the city, but still very close to town.  Very easy access from paved roads. This is a wonderful home sitting on 5 amazing acres.  Property is fully fenced.  The pasture has a piped fence and is crossed fenced, Horses are welcome.  The extra barn on the property is equipped with electric, running water and lighting!  Newer carpet down stairs, new Kitchen countertops. Close vicinity to great schools!  This is a MUST see!
